data.description: Welcome to this home on a quiet cul-de-sac in New Palestine with a top-rated school system. This beautifully maintained 2,996 sq ft. 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is well maintained including new HVAC and new windows in the last year! How about an open floorplan with an eat-in kitchen and a formal dining room, ideal for family meals or hosting dinner parties. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious master bedroom with cathedral ceilings and an ensuite bathroom with a huge walk-in closet. The 3 additional bedrooms are generously sized and share a full bath.
